name: Korean Air A330-223 [HL8211] Landing and Takeoff at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Korean Air returned to YYC again for a couple of charter flights this summer with their A330-200. Seen here is the first one, arriving runway 35L and departing 90 minutes later for Anchorage. ATC is included, and sorry about the shakiness. Enjoy!

Thanks for watching!
